{"tid":1497441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【機場禁制令】機管局稱未接獲反對　高院批准延長臨時禁制令","createTime":"2019-08-23T03:23:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T07:10:41.000Z","uid":25048,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fcdb96133591b91777347825760bb1139e9b252c","tid":1497441,"uid":25048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T03:23:32.000Z","msg":"早前有反《逃犯條例》示威者堵塞機場，機場管理局則於上周二（13日）獲高院批出臨時禁制令，限制任何人干擾機場正常使用。案件今（23日）在高院再訊，法官批准延長臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n原告為機場管理局，被告為非法和故意阻礙機場正常使用的人士。<br />\n<br />\n機管局今庭上透露，至今未有人提出反對臨時禁制令。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCA1471/2019<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/367054/%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4-%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F367054%2F%25E6%25A9%259F%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4-%25E6%25A9%259F%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%25B1%2580%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259C%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25B0%258D-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2599%25A2%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2587%2586%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E9%2595%25B7%25E8%2587%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%2588%25B6%25E4%25BB%25A4&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1YdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=818ce2d4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/367054/%E6%A9%9F%E5%A0%B4%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4-%E6%A9%9F%E7%AE%A1%E5%B1%80%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%AA%E6%8E%A5%E7%8D%B2%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D-%E9%AB%98%E9%99%A2%E6%89%B9%E5%87%86%E5%BB%B6%E9%95%B7%E8%87%A8%E6%99%82%E7%A6%81%E5%88%B6%E4%BB%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2cbb77a24490130415d07449c84a5421d6ca18d","tid":1497441,"uid":25048,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":4